  sections[5]{title,body}:
    Entry,"Open the repo and run npm install then npm run docs:generate npm run docs:check and npm run dev."
    Primary Flow,Create tasks with title priority due date tags and notes. Use filters to view active overdue and high priority work.
    Edit and Review,Mark tasks complete reopen or remove stale items. Use search to inspect active and completed entries.
    Documentation Workflow,Update TOON artifacts before behavior changes regenerate docs and rerun strict checks.
    Exit,Keep generated docs clean and rerun checks after every docs or UI change.
